name: The Final Gate
description:
The last journey we take in this life may or may not be the final journey of our existence. Where we go to, no one knows.

This is the Final Gate ... the Gate of Death. Which passage will you choose?

Digital sketch reworked via VQGAN+CLIP. MP4 loop with audio, 30 seconds, 23 MB. By @dehiscenceart, 2021
